The paper deals with image recognition using deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) for partially labeled data is a machine learning technique, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with food recognition, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
